title: Ep 10 | How & WHEN To MOVE ON | Divorce, Relationships
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description:
Sometimes we struggle with questions like "When is it time to move on?" "How will I know when I need to leave this relationship?" "How do I move on and heal from divorce?". Today in a super raw episode, we're going to talk about our own personal stories and HOW and WHEN we knew it was time to MOVE ON. Watch the episode on youtube! www.youtube.com/KristenxLeanne

We have a TON of book recommendations linked on the youtube video in the description box!
